test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (4 == 3)
 +  where 4 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x763181f38b80>([76])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x763181f38b80> = [[1, 76], [1, 76, 1], [1, 76, 1], [1, 76, 1, 76], [1, 76, 1, 76], [1, 76, 1, 76, 1], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 2888 == 76
 +  where 2888 = <built-in function prod>([4, 19, 38])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
